00:10:39,931 --> 00:10:43,113
of like wishful thinking and wishful features.

186
00:10:43,113 --> 00:10:48,057
You know, I had to kind of convince myself that even if I was obvious, even if a feature

187
00:10:48,057 --> 00:10:53,000
was obviously out of place, if I felt strongly enough about it, I thought that I would be

188
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:55,661
able, through some sort of gradual unconscious...

